#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:14
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kspread; Basics"
msgid "&sheets; Basics"
msgstr "Fundamentos de &kspread;"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:16
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Like the rest of &kde;, &kspread; is highly configurable, which can cause "
#| "problems for readers trying to compare the text in a document such as "
#| "this with what they see on the version of &kspread; running on their "
#| "desktop. To cut down on some of the possibilities for confusion, it it "
#| "suggested that when you first start to use &kspread; you set the default "
#| "options in all pages of the &kspread; configuration dialog (obtained by "
#| "selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "&kspread;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>) except for <guilabel>Completion "
#| "mode: </guilabel> in the <guisubmenu>Misc</guisubmenu> page, which should "
#| "be set to <guimenuitem>None</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Like the rest of &kde;, &sheets; is highly configurable, which can cause "
"problems for readers trying to compare the text in a document such as this "
"with what they see on the version of &sheets; running on their desktop. To "
"cut down on some of the possibilities for confusion, it is suggested that "
"when you first start to use &sheets; you set the default options in all "
"pages of the &sheets; configuration dialog (obtained by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Sheets...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Como o resto de &kde;, &kspread; é moi configurábel, o que pode dar "
"problemas aos leitores que tenten comparar o texto deste documento coa "
"versión de &kspread; que eles teñan no seu computador. Para evitar algunha "
"das posibilidades de confusión, recoméndase que cando comece a usar "
"&kspread; axuste aos valores predeterminados todos dos valores das distintas "
"páxinas do diálogo de configuración de &kspread; (obtido mediante "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Configuración</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configurar "
"&kspread;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>) excepto o <guilabel>Modo de "
"Completación:</guilabel> na páxina <guisubmenu>Diversos</guisubmenu>, que "
"debera ser posto como <guimenuitem>Nengún</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spreadsheets for Beginners"
msgstr "Follas de Cálculo para Novatos"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:29
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This section attempts to explain by example what a spreadsheet program "
#| "such as &kspread; actually does, and why it is such a useful tool in any "
#| "situation where you have to deal with numbers. If you have already used a "
#| "spreadsheet program you may wish to skip to the next section."
msgid ""
"This section attempts to explain by example what a spreadsheet program such "
"as &sheets; actually does, and why it is such a useful tool in any situation "
"where you have to deal with numbers. If you have already used a spreadsheet "
"program you may wish to skip to the next section."
msgstr ""
"Nesta sección tentarase explicar mediante exemplos o que fai realmente un "
"programa de follas de cálculo como &kspread;, e por que é unha ferramenta "
"tan útil en todos aqueles casos onde haxa que manexar números. Se xa ten "
"usado algún programa de follas de cálculo pode pasar para a próxima sección."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The first thing to do is to start up &kspread;. You can do this by "
#| "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on a &kspread; icon if there is "
#| "one on your desktop or panel, or you can select "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Office</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kspread;</guimenuitem> "
#| "</menuchoice> from the K menu."
msgid ""
"The first thing to do is to start up &sheets;. You can do this by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on a &sheets; icon if there is one "
"on your desktop or panel, or you can select <menuchoice><guimenu>Office</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&sheets;</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the "
"application launcher."
msgstr ""
"O primeiro é iniciar &kspread;. Pode face-lo premendo co botón "
"<mousebutton>direito</mousebutton> do rato no ícone de &kspread; se o hai no "
"seu escritorio ou panel, ou pode escoller <menuchoice><guimenu>Ofimática</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>&kspread;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> no menú K."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:47
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kspread; at first run"
msgid "&sheets; at first run"
msgstr "&kspread; ao comezar"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it has started you will be given the choice of opening a recent "
"document, creating a new document from a template (with templates "
"categories) or opening an existing document . Select the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> category on the left and choose the <guilabel>Blank Worksheet</"
"guilabel> template. Then click the <guibutton>Use This Template</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Cando arrinque daráselle a opción de abrir un documento recente, crear un "
"documento novo a partir dun modelo (con categorías de modelos) ou abrir un "
"documento xa existente. Escolla a categoría <guilabel>Xeral</guilabel> á "
"esquerda e escolla o modelo <guilabel>Folla de cálculo en branco</guilabel>. "
"Entón prema o botón <guibutton>Usar este Modelo</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:56
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Looking at &kspread; once it has started up, you will see a sheet of "
#| "empty rectangular cells arranged in numbered rows and lettered columns. "
#| "This is where you enter data or formula, text or charts."
msgid ""
"Looking at &sheets; once it has started up, you will see a sheet of empty "
"rectangular cells arranged in numbered rows and lettered columns. This is "
"where you enter data or formula, text or charts."
msgstr ""
"O aspecto inicial de &kspread; é unha o de un espazo de celas rectangulares "
"en branco dispostar en filas numeradas e columnas identificadas. Nelas é "
"onde ha introducir datos ou fórmulas, texto ou diagramas."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot starting1"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla do inicio 1"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Now, enter the text and values shown in the first 5 rows of the above "
#| "screenshot into the same cells of your spreadsheet. Ignore what is in row "
#| "7 for the moment. To enter anything into a cell first select the cell by "
#| "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking inside it, then type whatever "
#| "you want, then press <keycap>Enter</keycap> or use the arrow keys to move "
#| "the selection point to another cell."
msgid ""
"Now, enter the text and values shown in the first 5 rows of the above "
"screenshot into the same cells of your spreadsheet. Ignore what is in row 7 "
"for the moment. To enter anything into a cell first select the cell by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking inside it, then type whatever you "
"want, then press &Enter; or use the arrow keys to move the selection point "
"to another cell."
msgstr ""
"Agora, escriba o texto e os valores que se mostran nas 5 primeiras filas da "
"imaxe de arriba nas mesmas celas da súa folla de cálculo. Ignore por agora o "
"contido da fila 7. Para introducir algo nunha cela primeiro escolla a cela "
"premendo co botón <mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> do rato nela, logo "
"escriba o que sexa, e prema <keycap>Intro</keycap> ou use os cursores para "
"mover o ponteiro para outra cela."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:75
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "What we have entered so far could be a simple budget for the next two "
#| "months, listing how much we think we will be spending for Food, Shelter, "
#| "Clothing and any Other expenditure. Now select cell B7 (column B, row 7), "
#| "type in <userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> and press <keycap>Enter</"
#| "keycap>. Because it begins with a <keycap>=</keycap> symbol &kspread; "
#| "sees this as a formula, something it has to calculate, in this case by "
#| "adding together the values in the 4 cells B2 to B5, and what is shown in "
#| "the cell B7 is the result of that calculation."
msgid ""
"What we have entered so far could be a simple budget for the next two "
"months, listing how much we think we will be spending for Food, Shelter, "
"Clothing and any Other expenditure. Now select cell B7 (column B, row 7), "
"type in <userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> and press &Enter;. Because it "
"begins with a <keycap>=</keycap> symbol &sheets; sees this as a formula, "
"something it has to calculate, in this case by adding together the values in "
"the 4 cells B2 to B5, and what is shown in the cell B7 is the result of that "
"calculation."
msgstr ""
"O que levamos escrito pode ser un orzamento simples para os próximos dous "
"meses, cunha lista de canto cremos que vamos gastar en Comida, Ocio, Roupa e "
"calquer Outros gastos. Agora escolla a cela B7 (columna B, fila 7), escriba "
"nela <userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> e prema <keycap>Intro</keycap>. "
"Dado que comeza co símbolo <keycap>=</keycap> &kspread; ha-o interpretar "
"como unha fórmula, algo que debe calcular, neste caso somando os valores nas "
"4 celas da B2 á B5, e o que se mostra na cela B7 é o resultado de tal "
"cálculo."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:83
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You could enter a similar formula into cell C7, except that in this case "
#| "it would have to be <userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, but there is an "
#| "easier way which is to Copy cell B7 and Paste it into C7. &kspread; will "
#| "automatically adjust the cell references from B.. to C.. when the Paste "
#| "is done."
msgid ""
"You could enter a similar formula into cell C7, except that in this case it "
"would have to be <userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, but there is an easier "
"way which is to Copy cell B7 and Paste it into C7. &sheets; will "
"automatically adjust the cell references from B.. to C.. when the Paste is "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Pode escribir unha fórmula similar na cela C7, excepto que neste caso debe "
"somar <userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, pero é mais simples se Copia a "
"cela B7 e a Apega na C7. &kspread; axustará automaticamente as referencias á "
"celas de B… para C… cando faga o apegar."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "At this point you may think that &kspread; is doing no more than you "
#| "could manage with pencil, paper and a calculator, and you could be right, "
#| "but remember that this is a very small example of a spreadsheet, doing "
#| "simple calculations on only a few numbers. For any reasonably amount of "
#| "values or data using a spreadsheet to do the calculations is much quicker "
#| "and more accurate than doing them manually."
msgid ""
"At this point you may think that &sheets; is doing no more than you could "
"manage with pencil, paper and a calculator, and you could be right, but "
"remember that this is a very small example of a spreadsheet, doing simple "
"calculations on only a few numbers. For any reasonably amount of values or "
"data using a spreadsheet to do the calculations is much quicker and more "
"accurate than doing them manually."
msgstr ""
"Neste momento pode estar a pensar que &kspread; non fai mais que aquelo que "
"podería facer por si cun lapis, papel e unha calculadora, e pode estar no "
"certo, pero lembre que este é un exemplo moi pequeno de folla de cálculo, "
"con cálculos simples en só uns poucos números. Para calquer cantidade "
"razoábel de valores ou datos é moito mais rápido e exacto usar unha folla de "
"cálculo que face-lo á mao."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, a spreadsheet lets you play the <quote>What if?</quote> game. Because "
"each formula is automatically recalculated whenever any of the values it "
"refers to are changed, you can quickly see what happens if you alter any of "
"them. Using our example you can see the effect of reducing the amount spent "
"on food in December by just entering a new value into cell C2. If you had a "
"spreadsheet that modelled the greenhouse effect accurately you could perhaps "
"see the effect of a 50 percent reduction in the amount of methane released "
"into the atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"Ademais, coas follas de cálculo poderá xogar a <quote>Que pasaría se?</"
"quote>. Dado que as fórmulas son automaticamente recalculadas cada vez que "
"algún dos valores que usa cambia, pode ver rapidamente que ocorrerá se "
"altera calquera deles. Co noso exemplo pode ver o efecto de reducir o "
"importe gastado en comida en decembro se simplemente insire un valor novo na "
"cela C2. Se tivese unha folla de cálculo que modelase o efecto invernadoiro "
"quizais puidese ver o efecto dunha redución dun 50% na cantidade de metano "
"liberado á atmosfera."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Cells"
msgstr "Escoller Celas"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select a single cell or a rectangular area of cells in the "
"spreadsheet. The selected cell(s) are displayed with a thick black border."
msgstr ""
"Pode escoller unha cela simples ou unha área rectangular de celas na folla "
"de cálculo. As celas escollidas son destacadas cun bordo negro groso."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can select a single cell in one of the following ways"
msgstr "Pode escoller unha cela só das seguintes maneiras"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on it"
msgstr "prema co botón <mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> nela"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "enter the cell reference (for example <userinput>B5</userinput>) into the "
#| "cell reference box at the left end of the Formula toolbar and press "
#| "<keycap>Enter</keycap>"
msgid ""
"enter the cell reference (for example <userinput>B5</userinput>) into the "
"cell reference box at the left end of the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> "
"tool options and press &Enter;"
msgstr ""
"escriba a referencia da cela (por exemplo <userinput>B5</userinput>) na "
"caixa de referencia no estremo esquerdo da barra de ferramentas de Fórmula e "
"prema <keycap>Intro</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:115
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "use the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option"
msgid ""
"use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option"
msgstr ""
"use a opción do menú <menuchoice><guimenu>Vista</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ir "
"para a cela…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:119
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can also steer your way around with the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. "
#| "Pressing the <keysym>Enter</keysym> key will move the current selection "
#| "one position up, down, left or right depending on the setting in the "
#| "<guilabel>Misc </guilabel> page of &kspread;'s <link linkend=\"configmisc"
#| "\">configuration dialog box</link>."
msgid ""
"You can also steer your way around with the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. "
"Pressing the &Enter; key will move the current selection one position up, "
"down, left or right depending on the setting in the <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel> page of &sheets;'s <link linkend=\"configinterface\">configuration "
"dialog box</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tamén pode desprazarse cos <keysym>cursores</keysym>. Se preme a tecla "
"<keysym>Intro</keysym> moverase para unha cela cara riba, baixo, esquerda ou "
"direita dependendo de como estexa configurado na páxina <guilabel>Diversos</"
"guilabel> do <link linkend=\"configmisc\">Diálogo de configuración de "
"&kspread;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</keycombo> key down while "
"using the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys the selection will move to the start "
"or end of the block of occupied cells."
msgstr ""
"Se mantén a tecla <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</keycombo> premida á "
"vez que usa os <keysym>cursores</keysym> o punteiro moverase para o inicio "
"ou fin do bloque de celas ocupadas."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:127
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To select an area of contiguous cells drag the mouse cursor across the "
#| "desired area with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down, "
#| "or enter the references of the top left and bottom right cells separated "
#| "by a colon into the Formula toolbar cell reference box (for example "
#| "<userinput>B7:C14 </userinput>) and press <keycap>Enter</keycap>, or "
#| "enter these cell references in a similar format into the dialog box "
#| "brought up by <menuchoice><guimenu> View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto "
#| "Cell...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"To select an area of contiguous cells drag the mouse cursor across the "
"desired area with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down, or "
"enter the references of the top left and bottom right cells separated by a "
"colon into the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> cell reference box (for "
"example <userinput>B7:C14</userinput>) and press &Enter;, or enter these "
"cell references in a similar format into the dialog box brought up by "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Para escoller unha área de celas contiguas arrastre o cursor do rato sobre a "
"área desexada á vez que mantén premido o botón <mousebutton>esquerdo</"
"mousebutton> do rato, ou escriba as referencias das celas de riba á esquerda "
"e abaixo á direita separadas por dous puntos na caixa de referencia da barra "
"de ferramentas de Fórmulas (por exemplo <userinput>B7:C14</userinput>) e "
"prema <keycap>Intro</keycap>, ou escriba as referencias das celas nun "
"formato similar no diálogo que se mostra mediante <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Vista</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ir para a Cela…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select an area of cells by selecting the cell in one corner of "
"the wanted area then holding the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; </"
"keycombo> key down while using the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse "
"button to select the cell in the opposite corner."
msgstr ""
"Tamén pode escoller unha área de celas se escolle unha cela dunha esquina da "
"área desexada e mantén premida a tecla <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</"
"keycombo> mentres usa o botón <mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> do rato "
"para escoller a cela da outra esquina."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select non-contiguous cells, click on the first cell you want to select "
"then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> key and select "
"the other cells."
msgstr ""
"Para escolle celas non contiguas, prema a primeira que queira escoller, logo "
"manteña premida a tecla <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> e vaia "
"escollendo nas outras celas."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a complete row or column of cells <mousebutton>left </mousebutton> "
"click on the row number at the left of the worksheet or on the column "
"letters at the top. To select adjacent rows or columns drag the mouse "
"pointer over the appropriate row numbers or column letters with the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down."
msgstr ""
"Para escolle unha columna ou unha fila ao completo prema co botón "
"<mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> do rato no número da fila á esquerda da "
"folla ou na letra da columna por riba. Para escoller filas ou columnas "
"adxacentes arraste o rato sobre os números de fila ou as letras de columna "
"axeitadas co botón <mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> premido."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:149
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To select non-contiguous cells, click on the first cell you want to "
#| "select then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> key and "
#| "select the other cells."
msgid ""
"To select non-contiguous rows or columns of cells, click on the first row "
"number or column letter then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</"
"keycombo> key and select the other rows or columns of cells."
msgstr ""
"Para escolle celas non contiguas, prema a primeira que desexe escoller, logo "
"manteña premido <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> e vaia "
"escollendo nas outras celas."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Data"
msgstr "Inserir Datos"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:157
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Entering data into a cell can be as simple as selecting the cell, typing "
#| "your data, then pressing <keycap>Enter</keycap> or moving the selection "
#| "to another cell with one of the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. Depending on "
#| "how you enter the data, &kspread; will interpret it as a number, date, "
#| "time or text:"
msgid ""
"Entering data into a cell can be as simple as selecting the cell, typing "
"your data, then pressing &Enter; or moving the selection to another cell "
"with one of the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. Depending on how you enter the "
"data, &sheets; will interpret it as a number, date, time or text:"
msgstr ""
"Inserir datos nunha cela é tan simples como escoller a cela, escribir o "
"dato, e premer <keycap>Intro</keycap> ou moverse para outra cela cun dos "
"<keysym>cursores</keysym>. Dependendo do que escriba, &kspread; interpretara-"
"o como un número, data, hora ou texto:"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Numbers are entered in the obvious way; <userinput>123</userinput>, "
"<userinput> -123</userinput>, <userinput>456.7</userinput> or in scientific "
"notation <userinput>-1.2E-5</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Os números insírense como no papel: <userinput>123</userinput>, "
"<userinput>-123</userinput>, <userinput>456,7</userinput> ou en notación "
"científica <userinput>-1,2E-5</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dates should be entered in your <quote>System</quote> format, as defined in "
"the &systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu> "
"Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date &amp; Time</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> tab. If, for example, you are using the DD/MM/"
"YYYY form you should enter <userinput>30/03/2012</userinput> for 30th March "
"2012. Leading zeroes can be omitted from the day and month fields and only "
"the last one or two digits of the year need to be entered if the date is in "
"the current century, for example <userinput>9/1/9</userinput> for 9th "
"January 2009."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Times should also be entered using the <quote>System</quote> format. For "
"example if you are using a 12 hour clock then enter times in HH:MIN am|pm or "
"HH:MIN:SS am|pm format such as <userinput>9:42 am</userinput> or <userinput> "
"10:30:52 pm</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"As horas tamén deben introducirse no formato do <quote>Sistema</quote>. Por "
"exemplo, se está a usar un reloxo de 12 horas entón insira as datas no "
"formato HH:MIN am|pm ou HH:MIN:SS am|pm, por exemplo <userinput>9:42 am</"
"userinput> ou <userinput>10:30:52 pm</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:183
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kspread; defines any input data as <quote>text</quote> if it cannot "
#| "recognize the data as being a number, date or time."
msgid ""
"&sheets; defines any input data as <quote>text</quote> if it cannot "
"recognize the data as being a number, date or time."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; define calquer dato escrito como <quote>texto</quote> se non é "
"quen de recoñece-lo como un número, data ou hora."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:188
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "By default, &kspread; right justifies numbers, dates and times within a "
#| "cell and left justifies anything else. This can be a useful guide to "
#| "whether you have entered a date or time in the correct format. But "
#| "remember that how items are displayed can be changed by altering the "
#| "<link linkend=\"formatdata\">cell format</link>."
msgid ""
"By default, &sheets; right justifies numbers, dates and times within a cell "
"and left justifies anything else. This can be a useful guide to whether you "
"have entered a date or time in the correct format. But remember that how "
"items are displayed can be changed by altering the <link linkend=\"formatdata"
"\">cell format</link>."
msgstr ""
"Por omisión, &kspread; aliña á direita os números datas e horas nas celas e "
"á esquerda o resto. Isto pode ser útil para recoñecer se escribiu a data ou "
"hora no formato correcto. Pero lembre que pode alterar o xeito no que son "
"mostrados os ítens modificando o <link linkend=\"formatdata\">formato da "
"cela</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:194
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The main text entry box in the Formula toolbar provides an easy way of "
#| "editing the contents of a selected cell. Press <keycap>Enter</keycap> or "
#| "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the green tick mark when you are "
#| "happy with what you have entered, or click on the red cross to cancel "
#| "your edits."
msgid ""
"The main text entry box in the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> tool options "
"provides an easy way of editing the contents of a selected cell. Press "
"&Enter; or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the green tick mark when "
"you are happy with what you have entered, or click on the red cross to "
"cancel your edits."
msgstr ""
"A caixa principal de escrita na  barra de Fórmula fornece un xeito simples "
"de editar os contidos da cela escollida. Prema <keycap>Intro</keycap> ou "
"prema o botón <mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> na marca verde cando "
"remate o que estexa a escribir, ou prema a cruz vermella para cancelar a "
"edición."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Cell Format"
msgstr "Formato Xenérico da Cela"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kspread; uses the <quote>Generic</quote> cell format as default. As long "
#| "as this format is used, &kspread; autodetects the actual data type "
#| "depending on the current cell data. For example if you enter some text "
#| "into a cell and later enter a number into the same cell, &kspread; "
#| "automatically interprets the new data as a number. If you want to define "
#| "the type of data yourself, you can explicitly set it in the <link linkend="
#| "\"formatdata\">cell format</link>. You can change the format back to "
#| "<quote>Generic</quote> at any time."
msgid ""
"&sheets; uses the <quote>Generic</quote> cell format as default. As long as "
"this format is used, &sheets; autodetects the actual data type depending on "
"the current cell data. For example if you enter some text into a cell and "
"later enter a number into the same cell, &sheets; automatically interprets "
"the new data as a number. If you want to define the type of data yourself, "
"you can explicitly set it in the <link linkend=\"formatdata\">cell format</"
"link>. You can change the format back to <quote>Generic</quote> at any time."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; usa por omisión o formato <quote>Xenérico</quote> para as celas. "
"Mentres use este formato, &kspread; detectará automaticamente o tipo real "
"dos datos en función dos datos actuais da cela. Por exemplo se escribe algún "
"texto nunha cela e mais tarde un número na mesma cela, &kspread; "
"interpretará automaticamente o novo dato como un número. Se que definir por "
"si o tipo do dato, pode explicita-lo en <link linkend=\"formatdata\">formato "
"das celas</link> en calquer instante."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy, Cut and Paste"
msgstr "Copiar, Cortar e Pegar"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:219
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "At first glance, &kspread;'s <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>, "
#| "<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> "
#| "appear to be similar to these functions in other &kde; applications. "
#| "Having selected a cell or cells, you can choose <guimenuitem>Copy</"
#| "guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</"
#| "guimenu> menu or from the drop down menu you get by holding the "
#| "<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button down on a selected cell. "
#| "You can also use the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
#| "<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
#| "<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo>, then move the selection to the target "
#| "cell and choose <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> or press <keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>. However there are "
#| "some subtleties associated with these functions in &kspread; and these "
#| "are discussed below."
msgid ""
"At first glance, &sheets;'s <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> appear "
"to be similar to these functions in other &kde; applications. Having "
"selected a cell or cells, you can choose <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu or from "
"the drop down menu you get by holding the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button down on a selected cell. You can also use the shortcuts "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo>, then move the "
"selection to the target cell and choose <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> or "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>. "
"However there are some subtleties associated with these functions in "
"&sheets; and these are discussed below."
msgstr ""
"A primeira vista, o <guimenuitem>Cortar</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copiar</"
"guimenuitem> e <guimenuitem>Pegar</guimenuitem> de &kspread; parecen "
"similares ás mesmas funcións nos outros aplicativos de &kde;. Se escolleu "
"unha cela ou celas, poderá escoller <guimenuitem>Copiar</guimenuitem> ou "
"<guimenuitem>Cortar</guimenuitem> no menú <guimenu>Editar</guimenu> ou no "
"menú contextual que se obtén ao premer o botón <mousebutton>direito</"
"mousebutton> do rato na cela actual. Tamén pode usar os atallos <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> ou <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>, e moverse para a cela de "
"destino e escoller <guimenuitem>Pegar</guimenuitem> ou premer <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>. Porén hai algunhas "
"subtilezas nestas funcións en &kspread; que son explicadas a seguir."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a cell contains a formula then the formula itself is copied rather than "
"the displayed result, and if the formula contains a reference to another "
"cell, then that reference is changed by the <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> "
"operation to point to the cell that is in the same relative position as in "
"the original cell. For example if cell A2 contains the formula <userinput> "
"=B3</userinput> and is copied to C4, cell C4 will contain <userinput>=D5 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Se unha cela contén unha fórmula entón a fórmula en si é copiada, non o "
"resultado que se amosa, e se a fórmula contén unha referencia a outra cela, "
"entón esa referencia cambiarase na operación de <guimenuitem>Cortar</"
"guimenuitem> ou <guimenuitem>Copiar</guimenuitem> e <guimenuitem>Pegar</"
"guimenuitem> para apuntar á cela que está na mesma posición relativa á cela "
"orixinal. Por exemplo se a cela A2 contén a fórmula <userinput>=B3</"
"userinput> e a copia en C4, a cela C4 conterá <userinput>=D5</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:242
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This may seem to be a rather strange way of doing a copy, but 99 percent "
#| "of the time it is exactly what is wanted (if it is not then see the "
#| "section about <link linkend=\"absolute\">absolute cell references</"
#| "link>). For example in the simple shopping list shown below, cell D2 "
#| "should contain <userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, D3 should be "
#| "<userinput>=B3 * C3</userinput>, D4 should be <userinput>=B4 * C4</"
#| "userinput> and so on. Instead of having to enter a different formula in "
#| "each cell, you can just enter the first formula into D2 and then copy it "
#| "into the cells below, letting &kspread; adjust the cell references to "
#| "suit."
msgid ""
"This may seem to be a rather strange way of doing a copy, but 99 percent of "
"the time it is exactly what is wanted (if it is not then see the section "
"about <link linkend=\"absolute\">absolute cell references</link>). For "
"example in the simple shopping list shown below, cell D2 should contain "
"<userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, D3 should be <userinput>=B3 * C3</"
"userinput>, D4 should be <userinput>=B4 * C4</userinput> and so on. Instead "
"of having to enter a different formula in each cell, you can just enter the "
"first formula into D2 and then copy it into the cells below, letting "
"&sheets; adjust the cell references to suit."
msgstr ""
"Isto pode aparentar ser un xeito estraño de facer unha copia, pero o 99% do "
"tempo é exactamente o que se quere (se non é así, consulte a sección sobre "
"<link linkend=\"absolute\">referencias absolutas a celas</link>). Por "
"exemplo na lista de compras que se mostra en baixo, a cela D2 debera conter "
"<userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, D3 debera ser <userinput>=B3 * C3</"
"userinput>, D4 debera ser <userinput>=B4 * C4</userinput> e sucesivamente. "
"No canto de ter que escribir unha fórmula diferente en cada cela, pode "
"limitarse a escribir a primeira fórmula en D2 e copiala nas celas en baixo, "
"deixando que &kspread; axuste as referencias das celas."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot copy1"
msgstr "Captura de Pantalla copia1"

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying and Pasting Cell Areas"
msgstr "Copiando e Pegando Áreas de Celas"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the above example D2 can be copied into all three cells D3 to D5 at once "
"by just copying D2 then selecting the complete cell area D3:D5 before doing "
"the paste."
msgstr ""
"No exemplo de riba D2 pode copiarse en calquera das tres celas D3 a D5 dunha "
"vez simplesmente copiando D2 e escollendo a área de celas D3:D5 antes de "
"pegar."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A rectangular area of cells can be cut or copied in one operation by "
"selecting the area before doing the cut or copy. Then select the top left "
"corner cell of the area you want to paste into before doing the paste."
msgstr ""
"Pode copiar ou cortar unha área rectangular de celas dunha só vez escollendo "
"a área antes de facer o cortado ou copiado. Entón escolla a cela do canto de "
"riba á esquerda da área onde queira pegar antes de facelo."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cut or copy a rectangular area of cells, say B2:C3, and paste it into "
"a larger area such as A10:D13 the original pattern of cells will be repeated "
"to fill the target area."
msgstr ""
"Se corta ou copia unha área rectangular de celas, digamos B2:C3 e a pega "
"nunha área maior como A13:D13, o padrón orixinal das celas repetirase para "
"encher a área obxectivo."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:271
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kspread; also provides a <quote>Drag and Copy</quote> method for copying "
#| "cells down into other cells immediately below or to the right of the "
#| "original cell(s). To use this method select the cell(s) to be copied then "
#| "position the mouse pointer over the small black square at the bottom "
#| "right corner of the selected cell(s) so the cursor changes to a double "
#| "headed arrow. Then hold the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
#| "down while you drag the selected cell(s) as far as you wish. Note that "
#| "cell references in formulae are incremented according to the relative "
#| "position change. Absolute references are not changed."
msgid ""
"&sheets; also provides a <quote>Drag and Copy</quote> method for copying "
"cells down into other cells immediately below or to the right of the "
"original cell(s). To use this method select the cell(s) to be copied then "
"position the mouse pointer over the small black square at the bottom right "
"corner of the selected cell(s) so the cursor changes to a double headed "
"arrow. Then hold the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button down while "
"you drag the selected cell(s) as far as you wish. Note that cell references "
"in formulae are incremented according to the relative position change. "
"Absolute references are not changed."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; tamén fornece un método de <quote>Arrastar e Copiar</quote> para "
"copiar unhas celas noutras xusto en baixo ou á direita da orixinal. Para "
"usar este método escolla as celas a copiar e poña o ponteiro do rato sobre o "
"cadradiño negro no canto de baixo á direita da(s) cela(s) escollida(s) para "
"que o cursos mude para unha frecha de duas cabezas. Entón prema o botón "
"<mousebutton>esquerdo</mousebutton> do rato mentres arrasta as celas "
"escollidas a onde desexe. Lembre que as referencias a celas das fórmulas son "
"aumentadas de acordo ao cambio en posición sofrido. As referencias absolutas "
"non son alteradas."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Paste Modes"
msgstr "Outros Métodos de Pegar"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:284
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A cell may contain text, a value, or a formula, and may also contain "
#| "special font, border or background <link linkend=\"formatspread"
#| "\">formatting information</link>. &kspread; has special versions of Paste "
#| "that let you handle these items in different ways."
msgid ""
"A cell may contain text, a value, or a formula, and may also contain special "
"font, border or background <link linkend=\"formatspread\">formatting "
"information</link>. &sheets; has special versions of Paste that let you "
"handle these items in different ways."
msgstr ""
"Unha cela pode conter texto, un valor ou unha fórmula, pero tamén pode "
"conter <link linkend=\"formatspread\">información de formato</link> cun tipo "
"de letra especial, bordo ou un fondo. &kspread; ten varias versións de "
"Apegar que lle permiten xestionar estes ítens de diferentes maneiras."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:289
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>brings up the <guilabel> Special Paste</"
#| "guilabel> dialog box. By selecting the appropriate item from the top part "
#| "of this dialog you can choose to paste just <guilabel>Text </guilabel>, "
#| "the cell <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, any <guilabel>Comment </guilabel> "
#| "in the cell(s) or <guilabel>Everything without border</guilabel>. The "
#| "items in the bottom part of this dialog box allow you to do simple <link "
#| "linkend=\"sumspecialpaste\">arithmetic on an area of cells</link>."
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>brings up the <guilabel> Special Paste</guilabel> "
"dialog box. By selecting the appropriate item from the left part of this "
"dialog you can choose to paste <guilabel>Everything</guilabel>, just "
"<guilabel>Text</guilabel>, the cell <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, any "
"<guilabel>Comment</guilabel> in the cell(s) or <guilabel>Everything without "
"border</guilabel>. The items in the right part of this dialog box allow you "
"to do simple <link linkend=\"sumspecialpaste\">arithmetic on an area of "
"cells</link>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Editar</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apegado Especial…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> mostra o diálogo <guilabel>Apegado Especial</"
"guilabel>. Escolla o elemento que corresponda na parte de riba deste diálogo "
"para apegar só <guilabel>Texto</guilabel>, o <guilabel>formato</guilabel> da "
"cela, calquer <guilabel>Comentario</guilabel> que conteñan ou <guilabel>Todo "
"sen bordos</guilabel>. Os ítens da parte de baixo permitenlle facer "
"operacións <link linkend=\"sumspecialpaste\">aritméticas básicas nunha área "
"de celas</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Paste with Insertion...</guimenuitem> inserts the copied "
"cell(s) into the sheet by moving the cells that would otherwise be "
"overwritten a suitable number of rows of columns down or to the right. It "
"can also be used to insert complete copied row(s) or column(s) into the "
"worksheet."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Pegar con Inserción…</guimenuitem> insere as celas copiadas na "
"folla desprazando cara baixo ou cara á dereita as celas que doutra maneira "
"serían sobrescritas un número axeitado de filas de columnas cara abaixo ou á "
"dereita. Tamén pode usarse para inserir columnas ou filas copiadas por "
"enteiro na folla."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert and Delete"
msgstr "Inserir e Suprimir"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:310
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use the <keysym>Delete</keysym> key or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit </"
#| "guimenu><guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Text</guimenuitem> </"
#| "menuchoice> to remove the text, value or formula from selected cell(s), "
#| "row(s) or column(s) without affecting anything else."
msgid ""
"Use the <keysym>Del</keysym> key or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Contents</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> to remove the text, value or formula from selected cell(s), "
"row(s) or column(s) without affecting anything else."
msgstr ""
"Use a tecla <keysym>Supr</keysym> o <menuchoice><guimenu>Editar</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Limpar</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Texto</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> para eliminar o texto, valor ou fórmula das celas, filas ou "
"columnas escollidas sen afectar a mais nada."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:315
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To delete everything in the selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s), "
#| "including comments and special formatting, use <keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\"> &Shift;<keysym>Delete</keysym></keycombo> or choose the "
#| "<guimenuitem>Delete </guimenuitem> option from the <guimenu>Edit</"
#| "guimenu> menu or from the pop up menu you get when you "
#| "<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a selection."
msgid ""
"To delete everything in the selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s), including "
"comments and special formatting, choose the <guimenuitem>All</guimenuitem> "
"option from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Clear</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu or from the pop up menu you get when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a selection."
msgstr ""
"Para borrar todo nas celas, filas ou columnas escollidas, incluíndo os "
"comentarios e formatos especiais, use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keysym>Supr</keysym></keycombo> ou a opción <guimenuitem>Borrar</"
"guimenuitem> do menú <guimenu>Editar</guimenu> ou desde o menú contextual "
"que se mostra ao premer co botón direito nunha selección."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove selected row(s) or column(s) completely, use the "
"<guimenuitem>Delete Rows</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Delete Columns</"
"guimenuitem> options from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Para retirar as filas ou columnas por completo, use <guimenuitem>Eliminar as "
"columnas</guimenuitem> ou <guimenuitem>Eliminar as filas</guimenuitem> no "
"menú contextual que se amosa co botón <mousebutton>dereito</mousebutton> do "
"rato."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a cell or cells and choose <guimenuitem>Remove Cells... </"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button pop up "
"menu, you can then choose whether other cells in the worksheet will be moved "
"up or to the left to fill in the space left by the cell(s) you have chosen "
"to remove."
msgstr ""
"Se escolle unha ou máis celas e usa <guimenuitem>Retirar as Celas…</"
"guimenuitem> no menú contextual do botón <mousebutton>dereito</mousebutton> "
"do rato, poderá escoller se as outras delas da folla deben moverse para a "
"esquerda para preencher o espazo deixado polas celas que escolleu retirar."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to insert new, blank, row(s) or column(s) into the sheet, select "
"row(s) or column(s) where you wish the new row(s) or column(s) to be placed "
"and choose the <guimenuitem>Insert Rows</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Insert "
"Columns</guimenuitem> option from the <mousebutton> right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Se quere inserir filas ou columnas novas en branco na folla, escolla as "
"filas ou columnas onde queira pór as novas e use a opción "
"<guimenuitem>Inserir Filas</guimenuitem>, ou <guimenuitem>Inserir Columnas</"
"guimenuitem> do menú contextual do botón <mousebutton>dereito</mousebutton> "
"do rato."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert new cells into the worksheet by selecting the area where you "
"want them to appear then choosing the <guimenuitem> Insert Cells...</"
"guimenuitem> option from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"pop up menu. You will then be asked whether the existing cell(s) in the "
"selected area should be moved down or to the right to make room for the new "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"Pode inserir novas celas na folla de cálculo escollendo a área onde queira "
"que aparezan e logo escollendo <guimenuitem>Inserir Celas…</guimenuitem> no "
"menú contextual do botón <mousebutton>dereito</mousebutton> do rato. "
"Perguntaráselle se as celas xa existentes na área escollida deben "
"desprazarse cara baixo ou cara á dereita para facer sitio para as novas."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Sums"
msgstr "Somas Simples"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:346
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the first character in a cell is an equals sign (<keycap>=</keycap>) "
#| "&kspread; will take the cell contents to be a formula which is to be "
#| "calculated. The result of the calculation will be displayed in the cell "
#| "rather than the formula itself. For example, enter <userinput>=2+3</"
#| "userinput> into a cell and it should display <emphasis>5</emphasis>."
msgid ""
"If the first character in a cell is an equals sign (<keycap>=</keycap>) "
"&sheets; will take the cell contents to be a formula which is to be "
"calculated. The result of the calculation will be displayed in the cell "
"rather than the formula itself. For example, enter <userinput>=2+3</"
"userinput> into a cell and it should display <emphasis>5</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Se o primeiro carácter dunha cela é un signo de igualdade (<keycap>=</"
"keycap>) &kspread; considerará o contido da cela como unha fórmula que debe "
"ser calculada. O resultado do cálculo será mostrado na cela no canto da "
"fórmula en si. Por exemplo, escribe <userinput>=2+3</userinput> nunha cela e "
"ela mostrará <emphasis>5</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More usefully, a formula can contain references to other cells, so that "
"<userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> will calculate the sum of the values in cells "
"B4 and A3, and this calculation will be updated whenever cells B4 or A3 are "
"changed."
msgstr ""
"Unha fórmula pode conter referencias para outras celas, de tal xeito que "
"<userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> calculará a soma dos valores das celas B4 e "
"A3, e este cómputo actualizarase sempre que as celas B4 ou A3 se cambien."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as addition, a formula can make use of the <keycap>-</keycap> symbol "
"for subtraction, <keycap>*</keycap> for multiplication, and <keycap> /</"
"keycap> to perform division. The round bracket symbols <keycap>(</keycap> "
"and <keycap>)</keycap> can also be used as in normal algebra, so you could "
"enter more complex formulae such as <userinput>=((B10 + C3) *5 - F11) / 2 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ademais de somas, as fórmulas poden usar o símbolo <keycap>-</keycap> para "
"as restas, <keycap>*</keycap> para as multiplicacións, e <keycap>/</keycap> "
"para as divisións. Os parénteses <keycap>(</keycap> e <keycap>)</keycap> "
"poden usarse como na álxebra normal, polo que pode inserir fórmulas "
"complexas como <userinput>=((B10 + C3) * 5 - F11) / 2</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cells containing a formula will be marked with a small blue triangle at the "
"bottom left corner if the <guilabel>Show formula indicator</guilabel> check "
"box in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Sheet Properties</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> dialog is "
"checked."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:367
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kspread; also includes a large number of built-in functions for "
#| "applications such as statistical, trigonometrical and financial "
#| "calculations. Their use will be examined in more depth in a <link linkend="
#| "\"formulas\"> later section</link> of this manual, but if you are "
#| "interested at this stage choose <guimenuitem>Function...</guimenuitem> "
#| "from the <guimenu>Insert </guimenu> menu and take a look through the "
#| "<guilabel>Function </guilabel> dialog box that will be displayed.."
msgid ""
"&sheets; also includes a large number of built-in functions for applications "
"such as statistical, trigonometrical and financial calculations. Their use "
"will be examined in more depth in a <link linkend=\"formulas\"> later "
"section</link> of this manual, but if you are interested at this stage "
"choose <guimenuitem>Function...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Insert</"
"guimenu> menu and take a look through the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> "
"dialog box that will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; tamén inclúi un grande número de funcións incorporadas para "
"aplicacións tais como cálculos estatísticos, trigonometricos e financeiros. "
"O seu uso será explicado con maior profundidade nunha <link linkend="
"\"formulas\">sección posterior</link> deste manual, pero se está interesado "
"escolla <guimenuitem>Función…</guimenuitem> no menú <guimenu>Inserir</"
"guimenu> e vote unha ollada polo diálogo <guilabel>Función</guilabel> que se "
"mostrará.."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the time being, however, the <userinput>SUM</userinput> function may be "
"of interest as it calculates the sum of all values in a specified area of "
"cells. For example <userinput>=SUM(B4:C10)</userinput> calculates the sum of "
"all values in the cell area B4 to C10."
msgstr ""
"Por agora, a función <userinput>SUM</userinput> pode ser de interese xa que "
"calcula a soma de todos os valores nunha área indicada de celas. Por exemplo "
"<userinput>=SUM(B4:C10)</userinput> calcula a soma de todos os valores nas "
"celas da área B4 a C10."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:378
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If &kspread; displays a row of <keycap>#</keycap> symbols when you have "
#| "entered your formula this usually means that it cannot understand what "
#| "you have entered, but if the row of <keycap>#</keycap> symbols ends with "
#| "a small red arrow this just means that the cell is not wide enough to "
#| "display the complete result, in which case you should either make the "
#| "cell(s) wider or change their <link linkend=\"formatdata\">format</link> "
#| "so that the result does fit properly."
msgid ""
"If &sheets; displays <keycap>#VALUE!</keycap> when you have entered your "
"formula this usually means that it cannot understand what you have entered, "
"but if the row of symbols ends with a small red arrow this just means that "
"the cell is not wide enough to display the complete result, in which case "
"you should either make the cell(s) wider or change their <link linkend="
"\"formatdata\">format</link> so that the result does fit properly."
msgstr ""
"Se &kspread; mostra unha liña de símbolos <keycap>#</keycap> cando insira a "
"fórmula significa, polo xeral, que non comprende o que acaba de inserir, "
"pero se a liña de <keycap>#</keycap> remata nunha frecha vermella só "
"significa que a cela non é larga de abondo para mostrar o resultado ao "
"completo, neste caso debe ou facer as celas mais largas ou modificar o seu "
"<link linkend=\"formatdata\">formato</link> para que couva."

