"it as a template by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Create Template From Document</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Doing "
"this opens the <guilabel>Create Template</guilabel> dialog box. Enter a name "
"for your new template into the <guilabel>Name:</guilabel> text box and press "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The next time you start a new document by "
"choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or when you next start &sheets; the startup dialog window will "
"give you the option of creating the new document from your template."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Create Template</guilabel> dialog box also lets you choose a "
"different picture to be displayed above the template name in the startup "
"dialog window, and lets you save your templates under different group names, "
"which will appear as different pages in the dialog."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Templates are stored as <literal role=\"extension\">.kst</literal> files "
"under <filename>~/.kde/share/apps/tables/templates/</filename>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing a Spreadsheet"
msgstr "Imprimir Follas de Cálculo"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Printing a spreadsheet is basically done by selecting <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"which brings up &kde;'s common <guilabel>Print</guilabel> dialog box where "
"you can choose, among other options, the printer to be used, the number of "
"copies and whether all or only selected pages are to be printed."
msgstr ""
"Pode imprimir a folla de cálculo mediante <menuchoice><guimenu>Ficheiro</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Imprimir…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> o que amosará o "
"diálogo común de &kde; de <guilabel>Imprimir</guilabel> onde poderá "
"escoller, entre outras opcións, a impresora a usar, o número de copias e se "
"serán impresas todas ou só as páxinas que escolla."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:593
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "By default &kspread; will print all items in the current worksheet, but "
#| "you can restrict this by first selecting the area that you want to be "
#| "printed then choosing <guimenuitem>Define Print Range</guimenuitem> from "
#| "the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Print Range</"
#| "guisubmenu> </menuchoice> sub menu."
msgid ""
"By default &sheets; will print all items in the current worksheet, but you "
"can restrict this by first selecting the area that you want to be printed "
"then choosing <guimenuitem>Define Print Range</guimenuitem> from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Print Range</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> sub menu."
msgstr ""
"Por omisión &kspread; imprimirá todos os ítens na folla actual, pero pode "
"restrinxir isto escollendo primeiro a área que que imprimir e logo "
"<guimenuitem>Definir Rango de Impresión</guimenuitem> no submenú "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Formato</guimenu><guisubmenu>Rango de Impresión</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:598
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kspread; will print as many pages as are necessary to include all items "
#| "in the current worksheet. You can quickly see how a worksheet will be "
#| "spilt into separate pages for printing by checking the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu> View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Page Borders</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> box. The boundaries of each printed page will "
#| "then be marked by colored lines in the worksheet."
msgid ""
"&sheets; will print as many pages as are necessary to include all items in "
"the current worksheet. You can quickly see how a worksheet will be split "
"into separate pages for printing by checking the <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Page Borders</guimenuitem></menuchoice> box. The "
"boundaries of each printed page will then be marked by colored lines in the "
"worksheet."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; ha imprimir tantas páxinas como sexan precisas para incluír todos "
"os ítens na folla actual. Pode ver como se há dividir a folla en varia "
"páxinas se marca a opción <menuchoice><guimenu>Vista</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Mostrar os Bordos da Páxina</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Os "
"bordos de cada páxina impresa serán marcados por liñas de cores na folla."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a more detailed view of what is to be sent to the printer, including "
"anything you have asked to be included in the page headers and footers (see "
"below), choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print "
"Preview...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Para ver con máis detalle o que se enviará á impresora, incluíndo todo o que "
"quixese incluír na cabeceira e rodapé (consulte en baixo), escolla "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Ficheiro</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previsualización da "
"Impresión</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To improve the appearance of the printed output , you can change the fonts, "
"colors, borders and sizes of the cells in the worksheet, see the <link "
"linkend=\"formatspread\">Spreadsheet Formatting</link> section for more "
"details about how to do this."
msgstr ""
"Para mellorar o aspecto da saída impresa, pode cambiar os tipos de letra, "
"cores, bordos e tamaños das celas na folla de cálculo, consulte a sección "
"<link linkend=\"formatspread\">Formatar a folla de cálculo</link> para máis "
"detalles."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guilabel>Page Layout</guilabel> dialog box, invoked by "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Page Layout...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, to change the orientation of the printed pages, "
"the paper size (this should be suitable for your printer) and the size of "
"the page borders."
msgstr ""
"Tamén pode usar o diálogo <guilabel>Disposición da páxina</guilabel>, "
"invocada mediante <menuchoice><guimenu>Formato</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Disposición da páxina…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, para cambiar "
"a orientación das páxinas impresas, o tamaño do papel (isto debería ser "
"axeitado para a súa impresora) e o tamaño dos bordos das páxinas."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:621
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Ranges</guilabel> section of the <guilabel>Options </"
#| "guilabel> page of the <guilabel>Page Layout</guilabel> dialog box "
#| "provides an alternative way of restricting the printed output to just one "
#| "part of the worksheet and allows you to repeat selected column(s) or "
#| "row(s) on each printed page. This page also lets you select whether or "
#| "not to print the grid, comment indicators and formula indicators, objects "
#| "and charts. In the section <guilabel>Scale Printout</guilabel> you can "
#| "set a scalefactor or limit the number of pages for the print."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sheet</guilabel> provides more options. The <guilabel>Print "
"settings</guilabel> section lets you select whether or not to print the "
"grid, comment indicators and formula indicators, objects and charts. The "
"<guilabel>Repetitions on each page</guilabel> section allows you to repeat "
"selected column(s) or row(s) on each printed page. In the section "
"<guilabel>Scaling</guilabel> you can set a scalefactor or the page limits "
"for the print."
msgstr ""
"A sección <guilabel>Rangos</guilabel> da páxina <guilabel>Opcións</guilabel> "
"do diálogo <guilabel>Disposición da Páxina</guilabel> fornece unha maneira "
"alternativa de restrinxir a saída impresa para só unha parte da folla de "
"cálculo e permítelle repetir as columnas ou filas que escolla en cada páxina "
"impresa. Esta páxina tamén lle permite escoller se imprimir ou non a grella, "
"os indicadores de comentario e fórmula, obxectos e diagramas. Na sección "
"<guilabel>Escalar a Impresión</guilabel> pode indicar un factor de escala ou "
"limitar o número de páxinas a imprimir."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You may also find it helpful to globally <guilabel>Enable tooltips</"
#~ "guilabel> in &kcontrolcenter; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Appearance &amp; "
#~ "Themes</guimenu><guimenuitem>Style</guimenuitem></menuchoice> on the "
#~ "<guilabel>Style</guilabel> page."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tamén pode achar útil <guilabel>Habilitar axudas</guilabel> globalmente "
#~ "en &kcontrolcenter; en <menuchoice><guimenu>Aparéncia &amp; Temas</"
#~ "guimenu> <guimenuitem>Estilo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> na páxina "
#~ "<guilabel>Estilo</guilabel>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>Header &amp; Footer</guilabel> page of the <guilabel> Page "
#~ "Layout</guilabel> dialog box also lets you add text, including items such "
#~ "as the filename, date and page number to the header and footer, of each "
#~ "printed page."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "A páxina <guilabel>Cabeceira &amp; Rodapé</guilabel> do diálogo "
#~ "<guilabel>Disposición da Páxina</guilabel> tamén lle permite engadir "
#~ "textio, incluindo termos como o nome do ficheiro, data e números de "
#~ "páxina, na cabeceira ou rodapé de cada páxina impresa."
